#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"After entering the correct Opening Balance, you can simply select the corresponding product from your device and proceed to payment. This will allow you to choose a payment method from your pre-configured settings. \n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            In our case the customer is paying in exact cash.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"ຫຼັງຈາກປ້ອນຍອດເປີດທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກຜະລິດຕະພັນທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງຈາກອຸປະກອນຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ດຳເນີນ"
"ການຊຳລະເງິນ. ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານເລືອກວິທີການຊຳລະເງິນຈາກການຕັ້ງຄ່າທີ່ກຽມໄວ້. \n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            ໃນກໍລະນີຂອງພວກເຮົາ, ລູກຄ້າກຳລັງຊຳລະດ້ວຍເງິນສົດພໍດີ.<br/>"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.ir_ui_view_3241
msgid ""
"All our courses are from Monday to Friday. Each day we start at our diving "
"school at 10 a.m. and finish at 1:30 p.m."
msgstr ""
"ຫຼັກສູດທັງໝົດຂອງພວກເຮົາແມ່ນແຕ່ວັນຈັນເຖິງວັນສຸກ. ທຸກໆມື້ພວກເຮົາເລີ່ມຢູ່ໂຮງຮຽນດຳນ້ຳເວລາ 10 ໂມງເຊົ້າ ແລ"
"ະ ສິ້ນສຸດເວລາ 13:30 ໂມງ."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.homepage
msgid "An address must be specified for a map to be embedded"
msgstr "ຕ້ອງລະບຸທີ່ຢູ່ເພື່ອໃຫ້ແຜນທີ່ສະແດງຜົນ"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"And just like that you are ready to go! 🤩<br/>\n"
"            You can now follow up on leads and convert them into sales, set up your regular tours, host special events and sell them via your website or in person. <br/>\n"
"            <br/>"
msgstr ""
"ແລະ ພຽງແຕ່ເທົ່ານີ້ທ່ານກໍ່ພ້ອມແລ້ວ! 🤩<br/>\n"
"            ດຽວນີ້ທ່ານສາມາດຕິດຕາມຜູ້ທີ່ສົນໃຈ ແລະ ປ່ຽນໃຫ້ເປັນຍອດຂາຍ, ຕັ້ງຄ່າທົວປົກກະຕິ, ຈັດກິດຈະກຳ"
"ພິເສດ ແລະ ຂາຍຜ່ານເວັບໄຊ ຫຼື ດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ. <br/>\n"
"            <br/>"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.ir_ui_view_3241
msgid ""
"Any cancellations up to 7 days in advance of the course are fully refunded. "
"After that, we cannot offer any refund."
msgstr ""
"ການຍົກເລີກໃດໆກ່ອນເລີ່ມຫຼັກສູດ 7 ມື້ ຈະໄດ້ຮັບເງິນຄືນເຕັມຈຳນວນ. ຫຼັງຈາກນັ້ນ, ພວກເຮົາບໍ່ສາມາດຄືນເງິນໃຫ້ໄ"
"ດ້."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Apart from regular recurring activities that can be booked via the calendar, you can also set up more elaborate special events and offer them to your customers via the website. For example, at Adam Diver we also offer an Open\n"
"            Water Diver-certification course. This section will take you through building this experience from scratch."
msgstr ""
"ນອກຈາກກິດຈະກຳປົກກະຕິທີ່ສາມາດຈອງຜ່ານປະຕິທິນໄດ້ແລ້ວ, ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າກິດຈະກຳພິເສດທີ່ລະອຽດກວ່າ ແລ"
"ະ ສະເໜີໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າຜ່ານເວັບໄຊ. ຕົວຢ່າງ, ຢູ່ Adam Diver ພວກເຮົາກໍ່ມີຫຼັກສູດໃບຢັ້ງຢືນ Open Water "
"Diver. ສ່ວນນີ້ຈະນຳພາທ່ານສ້າງປະສົບການນີ້ຕັ້ງແຕ່ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.homepage
msgid "Book a dive trip"
msgstr "ຈອງທິບດຳນ້ຳ"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By clicking on this opportunity we open the corresponding opportunity. Once there, We can send a message via the button \"<strong>Send Message</strong>\" on top of the chatter to further qualify the request. Once we know\n"
"            everything we need, we can create a quotation by clicking on the smart button \"<strong>New Quotation</strong>\" on the top left."
msgstr ""
"ໂດຍການຄລິກທີ່ໂອກາດນີ້ ພວກເຮົາຈະເປີດໂອກາດທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ. ເມື່ອຢູ່ທີ່ນັ້ນ, ພວກເຮົາສາມາດສົ່ງຂໍ້ຄວາມຜ່ານປຸ່ມ "
"\"<strong>ສົ່ງຂໍ້ຄວາມ</strong>\" ຢູ່ດ້ານເທິງເພື່ອສອບຖາມຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມ. ເມື່ອພວກເຮົາຮູ້ທຸກຢ່າງທີ່ຕ້ອງກາ"
"ນແລ້ວ, ພວກເຮົາສາມາດສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໄດ້ໂດຍການຄລິກທີ່ປຸ່ມ \"<strong>ໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໃໝ່</strong>"
"\" ຢູ່ເບື້ອງຊ້າຍດ້ານເທິງ."

