"Just like with the private booking, we need to block our only boat as a final step to avoid double booking. As a faster alternative to the previously shown flow, we can also use the\n"
"            <strong>Resource Leaves-feature</strong>. <br/>\n"
"            To do so, we simply go to the <strong>Appointments-App</strong>, select <strong>Configuration</strong> and then <strong>Resource Leaves</strong>. Once there, select New, select the <strong>Resource</strong> and\n"
"            corresponding dates - you are now good to go! 🥳<br/>"
msgstr ""
"ເຊັ່ນດຽວກັນກັບການຈອງສ່ວນຕົວ, ພວກເຮົາຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງຈອງເຮືອລຳດຽວຂອງພວກເຮົາໄວ້ເປັນຂັ້ນຕອນສຸດທ້າຍເພື່ອຫຼີກ"
"ເວັ້ນການຈອງຊ້ຳຊ້ອນ. ເພື່ອເປັນທາງເລືອກທີ່ໄວກວ່າ, ພວກເຮົາສາມາດໃຊ້ຄຸນສົມບັດ <strong>Resource "
"Leaves</strong>. <br/>\n"
"            ໂດຍໄປທີ່ແອັບ <strong>Appointments</strong>, ເລືອກ <strong>"
"Configuration</strong> ແລະ <strong>Resource Leaves</strong>. ຈາກນັ້ນເລືອກ New, ເ"
"ລືອກ <strong>Resource</strong> ແລະ ວັນທີທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ - ພຽງເທົ່ານີ້ກໍ່ຮຽບຮ້ອຍ! 🥳<br/>"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Keep track of your stock and equipment in real time with the "
"<strong>Inventory </strong>app—automate restocking and monitor expiration "
"dates effortlessly."
msgstr ""
"ຕິດຕາມສະຕັອກ ແລະ ອຸປະກອນຂອງທ່ານແບບສົດໆ (real time) ດ້ວຍແອັບ <strong>Inventory</"
"strong>—ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ການສັ່ງຊື້ສິນຄ້າຄືນແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ ແລະ ກວດສອບວັນໝົດອາຍຸໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Link to an existing customer: opens a drop-down field with existing customer"
" names. Select a name to link this new quotation to an existing customer "
"record."
msgstr ""
"ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບລູກຄ້າທີ່ມີຢູ່: ຈະເປີດລາຍການຊື່ລູກຄ້າທີ່ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວ. ເລືອກຊື່ເພື່ອເຊື່ອມໂຍງໃບສະເໜີລາຄານີ້ກັບບັນທຶກລູກຄ້"
"າທີ່ມີຢູ່."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid "Managing On-Site Payments"
msgstr "ການຈັດການການຊຳລະເງິນຢູ່ສະຖານທີ່"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.homepage
msgid "Map"
msgstr "ແຜນທີ່"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Now that our boat is ready, we need to create the tour itself. Still in the Appointments app, we select <strong>Appointments</strong> and click on <strong>New</strong>. There we set the <strong>Duration</strong>,\n"
"            <strong>Schedule</strong> and assign the relevant <strong>Resources</strong>.<br/>\n"
"            Additionally we can choose whether we require up-front payment or wish to confirm every booking manually before booking a slot for our customers under the <strong>Options-Tab.</strong> Since we at Scuba Tours also provide our\n"
"            participants with equipment for their dives, we use the <strong>Questions-Tab</strong> to automatically ask relevant for information such as Shoe Size and Height upon booking."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອເຮືອຂອງພວກເຮົາພ້ອມແລ້ວ, ພວກເຮົາຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງສ້າງທົວ. ໃນແອັບ Appointments, ເລືອກ <strong>"
"Appointments</strong> ແລະ ຄລິກ <strong>New</strong>. ຈາກນັ້ນຕັ້ງຄ່າ <strong>ໄລຍະເວລ"
"າ</strong>, <strong>ຕາຕະລາງ</strong> ແລະ ກຳນົດ <strong>ຊັບພະຍາກອນ (Resources)</"
"strong> ທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ.<br/>\n"
"            ນອກຈາກນັ້ນ, ພວກເຮົາສາມາດເລືອກໄດ້ວ່າຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ຊຳລະລ່ວງໜ້າ ຫຼື ຕ້ອງການຢືນຢັນການຈອງ"
"ດ້ວຍຕົນເອງກ່ອນ ໃນ <strong>Options-Tab.</strong> ເນື່ອງຈາກພວກເຮົາ Scuba Tours ຍັງຈັດກຽ"
"ມອຸປະກອນດຳນ້ຳໃຫ້ຜູ້ເຂົ້າຮ່ວມ, ພວກເຮົາຈຶ່ງໃຊ້ <strong>Questions-Tab</strong> ເພື່ອຖາມຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຈຳເ"
"ປັນໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ ເຊັ່ນ: ຂະໜາດເກີບ ແລະ ສ່ວນສູງໃນຕອນຈອງ."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Now we validate the payment, and that's it! Congratulations, you just sold a dive tour! As a final step, you can choose send the receipt via mail or print it on the following screen. Please note that connecting your printer\n"
"            to the POS-App is also covered in our"
msgstr ""
"ດຽວນີ້ພວກເຮົາຢືນຢັນການຊຳລະເງິນ, ແລະ ກໍ່ຮຽບຮ້ອຍ! ຂໍສະແດງຄວາມຍິນດີ, ທ່ານຫາກໍ່ຂາຍທົວການດຳນ້ຳໄດ້! ຂັ້"
"ນຕອນສຸດທ້າຍ, ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກສົ່ງໃບບິນຜ່ານອີເມວ ຫຼື ພິມມັນອອກມາ. ກະລຸນາຮັບຊາບວ່າການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ເຄື່ອງພິມຂ"
"ອງທ່ານກັບແອັບ POS ແມ່ນມີຢູ່ໃນ"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as:"
msgstr "Odoo ມອບຄວາມເປັນໄປໄດ້ທີ່ບໍ່ສິ້ນສຸດໃຫ້ທ່ານ ເຊັ່ນ:"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo.com/trial"
msgstr "Odoo.com/trial"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once you are finished, you can edit the event description and related image on your website via the <strong>Go to Website-Smart Button</strong>. To make this event accessible to the whole wide world, simply change the ruler to\n"
"            <strong>Published </strong>and you good to go!"
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອສຳເລັດແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດແກ້ໄຂລາຍລະອຽດກິດຈະກຳ ແລະ ຮູບພາບທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງໃນເວັບໄຊຂອງທ່ານຜ່ານ "
"<strong>Go to Website-Smart Button</strong>. ເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ກິດຈະກຳນີ້ສະແດງໃຫ້ທົ່ວໂລກເຫັນ, "
"ພຽງແຕ່ປ່ຽນສະຖານະເປັນ <strong>Published</strong> ກໍ່ຮຽບຮ້ອຍ!"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once you are happy with the settings of your event, you can edit the corresponding page by clicking the <strong>Go to Website-Smart Button. </strong>Once you are happy with the end product, change the slider in the top menu to\n"
"            <strong>Published</strong> so it appears on your website. Now you can lean back and watch the bookings come in!"
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອທ່ານພໍໃຈກັບການຕັ້ງຄ່າກິດຈະກຳແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດແກ້ໄຂໜ້າເວັບທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງໄດ້ໂດຍການຄລິກ <strong>Go "
"to Website-Smart Button. </strong>ເມື່ອທ່ານພໍໃຈກັບຜົນງານສຸດທ້າຍ, ໃຫ້ປ່ຽນສະຖານະໃນເມນູດ້ານເ"
"ທິງເປັນ <strong>Published</strong> ເພື່ອໃຫ້ມັນສະແດງໃນເວັບໄຊ. ດຽວນີ້ທ່ານກໍ່ພຽງແຕ່ຖ້າເບິ່ງການຈອ"
"ງທີ່ກຳລັງເຂົ້າມາ!"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once you have configured your shop and decided what your customers can purchase on site, the rest is a breeze in the park.<br/>\n"
"            Simply click on your Point of Sale-App and select your \"Open Register\" under your Shop."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອທ່ານຕັ້ງຄ່າຮ້ານຄ້າ ແລະ ຕັດສິນໃຈແລ້ວວ່າລູກຄ້າສາມາດຊື້ຫຍັງໄດ້ແດ່ຢູ່ສະຖານທີ່, ສ່ວນທີ່ເຫຼືອກໍ່ຈະງ່າຍຫຼາ"
"ຍ.<br/>\n"
"            ພຽງແຕ່ຄລິກໃສ່ແອັບ Point of Sale ແລະ ເລືອກ \"Open Register\" ພາຍໃຕ້ຮ້ານຄ້າ"
"ຂອງທ່ານ."

