#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Simplify your finances with the seamlessly integrated "
"<strong>Accounting</strong> app."
msgstr ""
"ເຮັດໃຫ້ການເງິນຂອງທ່ານງ່າຍຂຶ້ນດ້ວຍແອັບ <strong>Accounting</strong> ທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັນຢ່າງຕໍ່ເນື່ອງ."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Since you are using the integrated website, your contact form is configured to automatically create an opportunity. <br/>\n"
"            A customer has filled it in and is inquiring about the possibility of a Family Dive - how exciting! This section will take you through all the steps to turn this request into a sale.<br/>\n"
"            First we open the <strong>CRM</strong>-App. There we see the new request in the stage New."
msgstr ""
"ເນື່ອງຈາກທ່ານກຳລັງໃຊ້ເວັບໄຊທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັນ, ແບບຟອມຕິດຕໍ່ຂອງທ່ານຈຶ່ງຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າໃຫ້ສ້າງໂອກາດໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັ"
"ດ. <br/>\n"
"            ລູກຄ້າໄດ້ປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນ ແລະ ສອບຖາມກ່ຽວກັບການດຳນ້ຳແບບຄອບຄົວ - ໜ້າຕື່ນເຕັ້ນຫຼາຍ! ສ່ວນນີ້ຈະນ"
"ຳພາທ່ານຜ່ານທຸກຂັ້ນຕອນເພື່ອປ່ຽນການສອບຖາມນີ້ໃຫ້ເປັນການຂາຍ.<br/>\n"
"            ທຳອິດພວກເຮົາເປີດແອັບ <strong>CRM</strong>. ທີ່ນັ້ນພວກເຮົາຈະເຫັນຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍໃໝ່ໃນຂັ້ນ"
"ຕອນ New (ໃໝ່)."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Some customers might spontaneously decide to join you for a tour or an "
"event, instead of booking online in advance. This is where the POS-App "
"shines, which allows your customer to simply pay on the spot and join the "
"fun."
msgstr ""
"ລູກຄ້າບາງຄົນອາດຈະຕັດສິນໃຈເຂົ້າຮ່ວມທົວ ຫຼື ກິດຈະກຳແບບກະທັນຫັນ ແທນທີ່ຈະຈອງອອນລາຍລ່ວງໜ້າ. ນີ້ຄືຈຸດເດັ່ນຂ"
"ອງແອັບ POS ເຊິ່ງຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າສາມາດຊຳລະເງິນຢູ່ສະຖານທີ່ ແລະ ເຂົ້າຮ່ວມກິດຈະກຳໄດ້ທັນທີ."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Store and organize client information in the <strong>Contacts </strong>app."
msgstr "ຈັດເກັບ ແລະ ຈັດລະບຽບຂໍ້ມູນລູກຄ້າໃນແອັບ <strong>Contacts</strong>."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Streamline billing and financial management with the <strong>Invoicing "
"app</strong>."
msgstr ""
"ປັບປຸງການອອກໃບບິນ ແລະ ການຈັດການທາງການເງິນໃຫ້ສະດວກຂຶ້ນດ້ວຍ <strong>ແອັບ Invoicing</"
"strong>."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Streamline team management and integrate employees into every process using "
"the <strong>Employees</strong> app."
msgstr ""
"ປັບປຸງການຈັດການທີມ ແລະ ລວມພະນັກງານເຂົ້າໃນທຸກຂະບວນການໂດຍໃຊ້ແອັບ <strong>Employees</"
"strong>."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.contact_us
msgid "Submit"
msgstr "ສົ່ງ"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>CRM App</strong> manages all customer relations, helps you keep "
"track of leads and website visitors and increase your sales."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແອັບ CRM</strong> ຈັດການທຸກຄວາມສຳພັນກັບລູກຄ້າ, ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຕິດຕາມຜູ້ທີ່ສົນໃຈ ແລະ ຜູ້ເຂົ້າຊົ"
"ມເວັບໄຊ ເພື່ອເພີ່ມຍອດຂາຍຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>POS App</strong> allows you to handle payments for walk-in "
"customers."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແອັບ POS</strong> ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດການການຊຳລະເງິນສຳລັບລູກຄ້າທີ່ມາໜ້າຮ້ານໄດ້."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Website App </strong>serves as your company's calling card, "
"allows customers to contact you and even purchase their aquatic adventures "
"from anywhere in the world."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແອັບ Website</strong> ເປັນຄືກັບບັດນາມສະກັດຂອງບໍລິສັດ, ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າສາມາດຕິດຕໍ່ຫາທ່ານ ແ"
"ລະ ແມ່ນແຕ່ຊື້ແພັກເກດການຜະຈົນໄພໃຕ້ນ້ຳໄດ້ຈາກທຸກຫົນທຸກແຫ່ງໃນໂລກ."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Customer field is <strong>not</strong> required on the opportunity form."
msgstr "ຫ້ອງລູກຄ້າ <strong>ບໍ່ໄດ້</strong> ບັງຄັບໃຫ້ປ້ອນໃນແບບຟອມໂອກາດ."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The final step in this flow is for us to reserve the relevant resource to ensure we don't get double booked - in the case our diving expedition it is our boat.<br/>\n"
"            To do so, we go to the <strong>Appointments-App</strong>, select <strong>Schedule </strong>and<strong> Resources Bookings. </strong>Then we click on the agreed upon date and fill the necessary information in the form\n"
"            <strong>.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"ຂັ້ນຕອນສຸດທ້າຍແມ່ນການຈອງຊັບພະຍາກອນທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນບໍ່ໃຫ້ມີການຈອງຊ້ຳຊ້ອນ - ໃນກໍລະນີການສຳຫຼວດດ"
"ຳນ້ຳຂອງພວກເຮົາກໍ່ຄືເຮືອ.<br/>\n"
"            ໂດຍໄປທີ່ແອັບ <strong>Appointments</strong>, ເລືອກ <strong>Schedule</"
"strong> ແລະ <strong>Resources Bookings.</strong> ຈາກນັ້ນຄລິກທີ່ວັນທີທີ່ຕົກລົງກັນ ແລະ ປ້ອນຂໍ້"
"ມູນທີ່ຈຳເປັນລົງໃນແບບຟອມ<strong>.</strong>"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr ""
"ສິ່ງເຫຼົ່ານີ້ແມ່ນໃຊ້ຟຣີໃນການສະໝັກໃຊ້ປະຈຸບັນຂອງທ່ານ; ເຊີນທົດລອງໃຊ້ໄດ້ເລີຍ! 🙃"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:appointment.resource,description:outdoor_activities.appointment_resource_1
msgid "This is our trusty ship"
msgstr "ນີ້ແມ່ນເຮືອທີ່ພວກເຮົາໄວ້ວາງໃຈ"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This package is ideal for any outdoor activity provider - from scuba diving to paragliding. Whether you want to reach out to customers, offer regular experiences or certification courses - This guide will help you manage\n"
"            your business more efficiently."
msgstr ""
"ແພັກເກດນີ້ເໝາະສຳລັບຜູ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິການກິດຈະກຳກາງແຈ້ງທຸກປະເພດ - ຕັ້ງແຕ່ການດຳນ້ຳ Scuba ຈົນເຖິງການຫຼິ້ນ "
"Paragliding. ບໍ່ວ່າທ່ານຈະຕ້ອງການຕິດຕໍ່ລູກຄ້າ, ສະເໜີປະສົບການປົກກະຕິ ຫຼື ຫຼັກສູດໃບຢັ້ງຢືນ - ຄຳແນະນຳນີ້ຈ"
"ະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຈັດການທຸລະກິດໄດ້ຢ່າງມີປະສິດທິພາບຫຼາຍຂຶ້ນ."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To be able to sell tickets for your events via your website, you need to go to<strong> Events -&gt; Configuration </strong>first and activate the feature <strong>Online Ticketing.<br/></strong>To allow the integration\n"
"                    of this flow with the <strong>Sales-App</strong>, you also need to activate<strong> Tickets with Sale</strong>."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອໃຫ້ສາມາດຂາຍປີ້ກິດຈະກຳຜ່ານເວັບໄຊ, ທ່ານຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງໄປທີ່ <strong>Events -&gt; "
"Configuration</strong> ກ່ອນ ແລະ ເປີດໃຊ້ຄຸນສົມບັດ <strong>Online Ticketing.<br/></"
"strong>ເພື່ອໃຫ້ສາມາດເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບ <strong>ແອັບ Sales</strong>, ທ່ານຍັງຕ້ອງເປີດໃຊ້ <strong>"
"Tickets with Sale</strong>."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid "To be sure to stay updated, follow us on"
msgstr "ເພື່ອໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າທ່ານຈະບໍ່ພາດຂ່າວສານໃໝ່ໆ, ຕິດຕາມພວກເຮົາໄດ້ທີ່"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To ensure that your POS is set up correctly, we strongly recommend following the step-by-step guide from our official documentation, which you can find linked below:<br/>\n"
"                    <br/>"
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນວ່າ POS ຂອງທ່ານຖືກຕັ້ງຄ່າຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງ, ພວກເຮົາຂໍແນະນຳໃຫ້ເຮັດຕາມຂັ້ນຕອນຈາກເອກະສານທາງກ"
"ານຂອງພວກເຮົາ ທີ່ລິ້ງດ້ານລຸ່ມນີ້:<br/>\n"
"                    <br/>"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To get started on our first event, we need to go to the <strong>Events-App </strong>and click on <strong>New</strong>. In the following form, we can set up all the key information, such as the date and duration of the event, the\n"
"            location and whether there is a limited number of participants. <br/>"
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອເລີ່ມຕົ້ນກິດຈະກຳທຳອິດ, ພວກເຮົາຕ້ອງໄປທີ່ແອັບ <strong>Events</strong> ແລະ ຄລິກ <strong>"
"New</strong>. ໃນແບບຟອມ, ພວກເຮົາສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າຂໍ້ມູນສຳຄັນ ເຊັ່ນ: ວັນທີ ແລະ ໄລຍະເວລາຂອງກິດຈະກ"
"ຳ, ສະຖານທີ່ ແລະ ຈຳນວນຜູ້ເຂົ້າຮ່ວມທີ່ຈຳກັດ. <br/>"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model:website.menu,name:outdoor_activities.website_menu_4
msgid "Top Menu for Website 1"
msgstr "ເມນູດ້ານເທິງສຳລັບເວັບໄຊ 1"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the<strong> Sales App</strong> to validate orders and create custom "
"quotations for special VIP bookings."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <strong>ແອັບ Sales</strong> ເພື່ອຢືນຢັນໃບສັ່ງຊື້ ແລະ ສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາສະເພາະສຳລັບການຈອງແ"
"ບບ VIP ພິເສດ."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid "Welcome to the <strong>Odoo Outdoor Activities Package!</strong>"
msgstr "ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບສູ່ <strong>Odoo Outdoor Activities Package!</strong>"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:outdoor_activities.knowledge_tour
msgid "Welcome! Happy exploring."
msgstr "ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບ! ຂໍໃຫ້ມ່ວນກັບການສຳຫຼວດ."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model:crm.tag,name:outdoor_activities.crm_tag_8
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.contact_us
msgid "Whatsapp"
msgstr "Whatsapp"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With the <strong>Events App</strong> you can create certification courses "
"and special Experiences for your customers."
msgstr ""
"ດ້ວຍ <strong>ແອັບ Events</strong> ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງຫຼັກສູດໃບຢັ້ງຢືນ ແລະ ປະສົບການພິເສດສຳລັບລູກຄ້າ"
"ຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With the <strong>Surveys</strong> app you can gather valuable customer "
"feedback and business insights to offer your customers the best experience "
"possible"
msgstr ""
"ດ້ວຍແອັບ <strong>Surveys</strong> ທ່ານສາມາດຮວບຮວມຄຳຄິດເຫັນທີ່ມີຄຸນຄ່າຈາກລູກຄ້າ ແລະ ຂໍ້ມູນທາງ"
"ທຸລະກິດ ເພື່ອມອບປະສົບການທີ່ດີທີ່ສຸດໃຫ້ກັບລູກຄ້າຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With the Outdoor Activities-Package you can offer regular experiences that your customers can conveniently book online. In our sample database, we offer diving outings on our trusty ship Deep Blue Something. As everyone of our\n"
"            expeditions requires our ship to get to the diving spot, our first step is to set up our ship. We do this by going to the <strong>Appointments-app </strong>and under <strong>Configuration</strong> selecting\n"
"            <strong>Resources</strong>. <br/>\n"
"            There we click on <strong>New</strong>. Since we want several guests on the same tour, we set this resource to <strong>shareable</strong> and set the <strong>capacity </strong>to the 10 seats we have on our boat - this\n"
"            means that we can have up to 10 participants per tour.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"ດ້ວຍ Outdoor Activities-Package ທ່ານສາມາດສະເໜີປະສົບການປົກກະຕິທີ່ລູກຄ້າສາມາດຈອງອອນລາຍໄດ້ຢ່"
"າງສະດວກ. ໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງຂອງພວກເຮົາ, ພວກເຮົາສະເໜີການດຳນ້ຳດ້ວຍເຮືອ Deep Blue "
"Something. ເນື່ອງຈາກທຸກການສຳຫຼວດຕ້ອງໃຊ້ເຮືອເພື່ອໄປຫາຈຸດດຳນ້ຳ, ຂັ້ນຕອນທຳອິດແມ່ນການຕັ້ງຄ່າເຮືອ. ພວ"
"ກເຮົາເຮັດສິ່ງນີ້ໂດຍການໄປທີ່ແອັບ <strong>Appointments</strong> ແລະ ພາຍໃຕ້ <strong>"
"Configuration</strong> ເລືອກ <strong>Resources</strong>. <br/>\n"
"            ຈາກນັ້ນຄລິກ <strong>New</strong>. ເນື່ອງຈາກພວກເຮົາຕ້ອງການແຂກຫຼາຍຄົນໃນທົວດຽວ"
"ກັນ, ພວກເຮົາຈຶ່ງຕັ້ງຄ່າຊັບພະຍາກອນນີ້ເປັນ <strong>shareable (ແບ່ງປັນໄດ້)</strong> ແລະ ຕັ້ງຄ່າ "
"<strong>capacity (ຄວາມຈຸ)</strong> ເປັນ 10 ບ່ອນນັ່ງຕາມທີ່ມີໃນເຮືອ - ໝາຍຄວາມວ່າພວກເຮົາສາມ"
